{"tid":761104,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大公司MNC top sales，可能幫到你手","createTime":"2018-07-30T06:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T02:11:09.000Z","uid":51443,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ac63e75d447c1952045694d4ff819e1084b37546","tid":761104,"uid":51443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"Hello 小弟90後 由大學part time 到畢業都係做sales related 既工，由係luxury brand 做b2c 到MNC b2b top sales 都叫有d 方法<br />\n<br />\n由洗樓 電話cold call 不斷搵客 到 賣幾m 野比fortune 500 既公司，都有唔同技巧<br />\n<br />\n呢個post 唔係想教咩sales 技巧，係想幫下1d 小本經營 或者 見到好多人有好好idea / run緊既生意 但唔識做銷售 甚止平時行手作市集仔 都覺得坐係到既店主/員工可以做到d野（銷售）黎提高生意<br />\n<br />\n大家做過b2b sales 都應該知我地好多時間淨，所以激發起想係到睇下有無人做緊小生意 startup 想搵人part time / freelance 形式做銷售， 唔會收好多錢，有挑戰性既生意都想試，因為小弟係一個勁中意見客既人<br />\n<br />\n大家可以交換下諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（不過想知呢到係咪多中學生，無咩8090後創業）"},{"pid":"f0a481231fc044904d2b2f95258e45f727c7865c","tid":761104,"uid":101555,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"幾m野好少<br />\nMnc b2b sales起馬都億億聲"},{"pid":"3f0345ff780951e1aa27991fc3647ac3486fdc18","tid":761104,"uid":165377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"有冇野教下<br />\n純粹想聽"},{"pid":"a874908adbcbe588d9b93ae39b76e88b56d997b2","tid":761104,"uid":51443,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ac63e75d447c1952045694d4ff819e1084b37546","tid":761104,"uid":51443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"Hello 小弟90後 由大學part time 到畢業都係做sales related 既工，由係luxury brand 做b2c 到MNC b2b top sales 都叫有d 方法<br />\n<br />\n由洗樓 電話cold call 不斷搵客 到 賣幾m 野比fortune 500 既公司，都有唔同技巧<br />\n<br />\n呢個post 唔係想教咩sales 技巧，係想幫下1d 小本經營 或者 見到好多人有好好idea / run緊既生意 但唔識做銷售 甚止平時行手作市集仔 都覺得坐係到既店主/員工可以做到d野（銷售）黎提高生意<br />\n<br />\n大家做過b2b sales 都應該知我地好多時間淨，所以激發起想係到睇下有無人做緊小生意 startup 想搵人part time / freelance 形式做銷售， 唔會收好多錢，有挑戰性既生意都想試，因為小弟係一個勁中意見客既人<br />\n<br />\n大家可以交換下諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n（不過想知呢到係咪多中學生，無咩8090後創業）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"B2C 簡單黎講 因為客走左無得搵番，所以由個客埋黎就要觀察，望佢打扮，隻眼望邊，再加簡單問題 睇佢對答 估佢目的 有無興趣 然後先做selling <br />\n<br />\n有人話做sales 把口叻就得，旺中個d 賣幾十蚊野舖頭仔可能係既"},{"pid":"18d5003089b699bd47f7c31afc8257b6acd7d2fb","tid":761104,"uid":51443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0a481231fc044904d2b2f95258e45f727c7865c","tid":761104,"uid":101555,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"幾m野好少<br />\nMnc b2b sales起馬都億億聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:21:38.000Z","msg":"正喎，有咩 真心想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e56157f5ed388af24b9f0f0290d3eea09c8723","tid":761104,"uid":51443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f0345ff780951e1aa27991fc3647ac3486fdc18","tid":761104,"uid":165377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"有冇野教下<br />\n純粹想聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"想聽咩 b2c b2b 電話傾 都有唔同"},{"pid":"1f5c2e0f38c5d00272cc0ff77f62b32c90a0fe80","tid":761104,"uid":60017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0a481231fc044904d2b2f95258e45f727c7865c","tid":761104,"uid":101555,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"幾m野好少<br />\nMnc b2b sales起馬都億億聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:25:32.000Z","msg":"視乎公司嘅product，有時幾m嘢啲margin高，公司反而會拆得多佣俾sales"},{"pid":"ba69a6a92783d76850a44f2b58004e1d51c41230","tid":761104,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:30:36.000Z","msg":"有無 start up  pitching 經驗？"},{"pid":"9946f3ffde8be614ef79abad470a3eb3ac162013","tid":761104,"uid":51443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":